I"u<h1 id="fix-get-rid-of-the-black-borders--assetto-corsa">fix: get rid of the black borders :: Assetto Corsa</h1>

<p>I finally figured out how to get rid of the black borders by going into this location</p>

<p>C:\Users\User Name\Documents\Assetto Corsa\cfg and opening the video.ini file and adding</p>

<p>[REFRESH]</p>

<p>VALUE=60</p>

<p>below the video settings.</p>
